trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref>, <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart"></xref>, and <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Fornece suporte de momento da conceção para <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref>, <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart"> </xref>, e <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart"> </xref> controlos.

trans-unit.source: CatalogPartDesigner is a multi-purpose designer that provides design-time rendering for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart> controls, which both inherit from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> base class.
trans-unit.target: CatalogPartDesigner é um designer de objetivo multi que fornece a composição do momento da conceção para <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart>e <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart>controlos, que ambos os herdam da <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>base de classe.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: CatalogPartDesigner serves as a standard control designer, adding only what customization is needed to validate the associated control and apply its design mode state to the design-time rendering.
trans-unit.target: CatalogPartDesigner serve como um designer de controlo padrão, adicionar apenas que personalização é necessário validar o controlo associado e aplicar o estado do modo de design para a composição do momento da concepção.

trans-unit.source: If you have a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart> control, you can create a derived designer, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner>, to provide design-time rendering.
trans-unit.target: Se tiver um personalizado <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart>controlo, pode criar um designer derivado, tal como <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner>, para fornecer a composição do momento da concepção.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PageCatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: You can safely override any of the members as needed; however, when overriding the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner.CreateViewControl%2A> method, be sure to call the base implementation to avoid losing design mode state information.
trans-unit.target: Em segurança pode substituir qualquer um dos membros conforme necessário; No entanto, ao substituir o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner.CreateViewControl%2A>método, certifique-se chamar a implementação base para evitar a perda de informações de estado do modo de estrutura.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner.CreateViewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Creates a copy of the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> control to render at design time.
trans-unit.target: Cria uma cópia da associada <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref> controlo a compor no momento da concepção.

trans-unit.source: This method is overridden to copy zone information to the view control.
trans-unit.target: Este método é substituído para copiar a informação de zona para o controlo de vista.

trans-unit.source: A copy of the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref> control.

Verifies that the control resides in a zone of type <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"></xref>, and then gets the markup that is used to represent the control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Verifica se o controlo reside numa zona de tipo <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"> </xref>e, em seguida, obtém a marcação que é utilizada para representar o controlo no momento da concepção.

trans-unit.source: The markup that is used to represent the control at design time, or error markup if the control does not reside in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: O markup que é utilizada para representar o controlo no momento da conceção ou markup de erro se o controlo não reside num <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogZoneBase"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Binds the designer to the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref>-derived control.
trans-unit.target: Vincula o estruturador para associada <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref>-derivada do controlo.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"></xref>-derived control associated with the designer.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart"> </xref>-derivada do controlo associado o estruturador.
